testcase.name: PUT - set a news in review (Status: SUBMITTED -> IN REVIEW)
PUT - reject a news (Status: IN REVIEW -> REJECTED )
PUT - send rejected news back to jornalist (Status: REJECTED -> DRAFT )
DELETE - delete news in review (Status: IN REVIEW -> DELETED)
PUT - edit a news (Status: IN REVIEW -> EDITED)
PUT - edit a news (Status: EDITED -> EDITED)
PUT - set edited news back to review (Status: EDITED -> IN REVIEW )
PUT - schedule the publication of a news (Status: IN REVIEW -> SCHEDULED)
PUT - publish a news (Status: SCHEDULED -> PUBLISHED)
PUT - send published news back to review (Status: PUBLISHED -> IN REVIEW)
PUT - archive a news (Status: PUBLISHED -> ARCHIVED)
PUT - delete archived news (Status: ARCHIVED -> DELETED)
PUT - publish archived news (Status: ARCHIVED -> PUBLISHED)
